flowchart LR

    Client["Web Client"]

    subgraph CloudFns["Firebase Cloud Functions (Modular Monolith)"]
        direction TB
        ApiLayer["HTTP API Layer<br/>onRequest endpoints"]
        AIServices["Chat + Study Generation<br/>chat, studyCoach, studyGenerate,<br/>flashcardReview"]
        FocusServices["Focus + Gamification<br/>focusStart, focusStop,<br/>reward application"]
        MaterialServices["Material Ingestion + Retrieval<br/>materialIndex, materialDelete,<br/>chunk indexing"]
        SessionStore["Session Persistence Adapter<br/>Genkit session store"]

        ApiLayer --> AIServices
        ApiLayer --> FocusServices
        ApiLayer --> MaterialServices
        ApiLayer --> SessionStore
    end

    subgraph Persistence["Persistence"]
        direction TB
        FirestoreCore[("Firestore Core Data<br/>courses, chats, messages,<br/>focus/study documents")]
        FirestoreInternal[("Firestore Internal Collections<br/>material_chunks, genkit_sessions")]
        Storage[("Cloud Storage<br/>uploaded source files")]
    end

    subgraph ExternalAI["External AI"]
        direction TB
        OpenAI(["OpenAI API<br/>Genkit + OCR calls"])
    end

    Client -->|HTTPS calls| ApiLayer

    AIServices <-->|chats, messages,<br/>study sets, reviews| FirestoreCore
    AIServices -->|session history| FirestoreInternal
    SessionStore <-->|genkit_sessions| FirestoreInternal

    FocusServices <-->|focus sessions,<br/>summaries, gamification| FirestoreCore

    MaterialServices <-->|materials metadata| FirestoreCore
    MaterialServices <-->|material_chunks| FirestoreInternal
    MaterialServices <-->|read / delete files| Storage

    AIServices -->|generation| OpenAI
    MaterialServices -->|image OCR| OpenAI

